GSD.description:
dpaa2-switch: Fix memory leak in dpaa2_switch_acl_entry_add() and dpaa2_switch_acl_entry_remove()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.13 by commit 785ee7a82297e1512d9061aae91699212ed65796, it was introduced in version v5.13 by commit 1110318d83e8011c4dfcb2f7dd343bcfb1623c5f. For more details please see the references link.
